Provision is always there when you're

00:32:41.600 --> 00:32:49.199
attached to where He's at.

00:32:45.600 --> 00:32:52.639
Fruit is always bountiful whenever

00:32:49.200 --> 00:32:56.480
you're attached to Him.

00:32:52.640 --> 00:33:01.039
There is no lack; there is no lack of

00:32:56.480 --> 00:33:04.640
abundance. The

00:33:01.039 --> 00:33:07.360
Lord said, 'Where I am, the treasure is.'Where

00:33:04.640 --> 00:33:10.000
the anointing flows, where

00:33:07.360 --> 00:33:12.240
the anointing goes, where

00:33:10.000 --> 00:33:15.279
that covering goes, the blessing was

00:33:12.240 --> 00:33:18.559
there to take care of My people. Read—you

00:33:15.279 --> 00:33:20.640
know what, baby? Read that.

00:33:18.559 --> 00:33:23.678
Let's look at it.

00:33:20.640 --> 00:33:26.559
Do I have it there? Let's

00:33:23.679 --> 00:33:29.200
take a pause right here and look

00:33:26.559 --> 00:33:31.360
at that.

00:33:29.200 --> 00:33:35.799
Where's my history on that?

00:33:38.240 --> 00:33:43.200
It was Numbers.

00:33:41.039 --> 00:33:44.960
Yeah, read it. Can you read it

00:33:43.200 --> 00:33:45.760
loud?

00:33:44.960 --> 00:33:47.279
The passage?

00:33:45.760 --> 00:33:48.080
No, just the scripture.

00:33:47.279 --> 00:33:52.919
Yeah,

00:33:48.080 --> 00:33:52.918
Numbers 9:17-23:

00:33:56.320 --> 00:34:01.678
'And wherever and whenever the cloud was

00:33:58.799 --> 00:34:04.080
taken up from over the tabernacle, after

00:34:01.679 --> 00:34:06.640
that the children of Israel journeyed;

00:34:04.080 --> 00:34:08.719
and in the place where the cloud abode,

00:34:06.640 --> 00:34:11.520
there the children of Israel pitched

00:34:08.719 --> 00:34:13.918
their tents. At the commandment of the

00:34:11.520 --> 00:34:15.679
Lord the children of Israel journeyed,

00:34:13.918 --> 00:34:18.638
and at the commandment of the Lord they

00:34:15.679 --> 00:34:21.200
pitched. As long as the cloud abode

00:34:18.639 --> 00:34:23.679
upon the tabernacle they rested in

00:34:21.199 --> 00:34:26.399
their tents. And when the cloud tarried

00:34:23.679 --> 00:34:28.399
upon the tabernacle many days, then the

00:34:26.399 --> 00:34:31.759
children of Israel kept the charge of

00:34:28.399 --> 00:34:34.399
the Lord and journeyed not. And so it

00:34:31.760 --> 00:34:37.200
was, when the cloud abode from even unto

00:34:34.399 --> 00:34:39.440
the morning, and that the cloud was

00:34:37.199 --> 00:34:42.638
taken up in the morning, then they

00:34:39.440 --> 00:34:45.359
journeyed; whether it were two days, or a

00:34:42.639 --> 00:34:47.359
month, or a year, that the cloud tarried

00:34:45.359 --> 00:34:49.199
upon the tabernacle, the children of

00:34:47.359 --> 00:34:52.399
Israel abode in their tents, and

00:34:49.199 --> 00:34:54.719
journeyed not: but when it was taken up,

00:34:52.399 --> 00:34:56.719
they journeyed. At the commandment of

00:34:54.719 --> 00:34:58.480
the Lord they rested in the tents, and

00:34:56.719 --> 00:34:59.680
at the commandment of the Lord they

00:34:58.480 --> 00:35:03.680
journeyed.'You

00:34:59.680 --> 00:35:05.200
always stay where

00:35:03.680 --> 00:35:08.399
He's at.

00:35:05.200 --> 00:35:09.919
And where He's at, there's blessing.

00:35:08.400 --> 00:35:11.680
That's what the Lord was showing me

00:35:09.920 --> 00:35:13.920
today. I prayed a lot about this

00:35:11.680 --> 00:35:17.680
today, and He was showing me

00:35:13.920 --> 00:35:19.359
where the cloud is. It may

00:35:17.680 --> 00:35:20.640
not feel like it was where it was

00:35:19.359 --> 00:35:22.960
before—where

00:35:20.640 --> 00:35:26.640
your assignment

00:35:22.960 --> 00:35:29.200
changes, where God has you changes

00:35:26.640 --> 00:35:31.759
the direction of ministry.

00:35:29.200 --> 00:35:34.240
No matter if your flesh feels

00:35:31.760 --> 00:35:35.920
good about it or not,

00:35:34.240 --> 00:35:36.640
go where the cloud

00:35:35.920 --> 00:35:39.359
is.

00:35:36.640 --> 00:35:43.359
And where the cloud is, the provision is.

00:35:39.359 --> 00:35:45.279
God will always abundantly supply

00:35:43.359 --> 00:35:48.240
for that season when you're underneath

00:35:45.280 --> 00:35:49.920
that cloud. He said, 'There is no lack

00:35:48.240 --> 00:35:52.640
in Me. There is a lack of boldness.'You'll

00:35:49.920 --> 00:35:54.160
see; He told me that

00:35:52.640 --> 00:35:57.200
very strongly. He said, 'Brenda, there'll

00:35:54.160 --> 00:35:59.040
be no lack in this end-time move.'As

00:35:57.200 --> 00:36:01.680
I've been praying these last three days,

00:35:59.040 --> 00:36:05.119
He said, 'I'm putting in

00:36:01.680 --> 00:36:09.598
My dream team.'He

00:36:05.119 --> 00:36:12.240
said, 'Do you remember the

00:36:09.599 --> 00:36:15.839
Olympics when Michael Jordan, Scottie Pippen,

00:36:12.240 --> 00:36:17.919
and Larry Bird—the

00:36:15.839 --> 00:36:20.078
best dream team ever? They

00:36:17.920 --> 00:36:22.640
try to make a dream team now, but nobody

00:36:20.079 --> 00:36:25.680
compares to the original dream team back in the '90s

00:36:22.640 --> 00:36:27.520
when

00:36:25.680 --> 00:36:29.200
Michael Jordan and the others were whipping up

00:36:27.520 --> 00:36:31.040
on the nations. It was amazing.

00:36:29.200 --> 00:36:32.720
I'm a basketball fan; I love basketball.

00:36:31.040 --> 00:36:35.040
But I'm going to

00:36:32.720 --> 00:36:37.439
tell you, there was no dream team like

00:36:35.040 --> 00:36:41.520
that dream team.

00:36:37.440 --> 00:36:43.040
I mean, even with King James and

00:36:41.520 --> 00:36:44.880
what we have now with Stephen Curry,

00:36:43.040 --> 00:36:48.880
it's a joke compared to the

00:36:44.880 --> 00:36:53.599
last dream team in my opinion.

00:36:48.880 --> 00:36:56.800
The Lord said William Branham, Jack Coe, Oral

00:36:53.599 --> 00:36:59.040
Roberts, and Kathryn Kuhlman were my '40s

00:36:56.800 --> 00:37:00.480
dream team.

00:36:59.040 --> 00:37:03.759
There was a dream team for that

00:37:00.480 --> 00:37:05.839
generation. But I'm raising up My final

00:37:03.760 --> 00:37:07.839
generation, My dream team of this generation.'And

00:37:05.839 --> 00:37:09.920
there are certain people

00:37:07.839 --> 00:37:12.078
that you're about to see, Brandon, if

00:37:09.920 --> 00:37:14.800
you'll just say yes—that

00:37:12.079 --> 00:37:17.839
the glory of God will

00:37:14.800 --> 00:37:22.320
radiate out of you like Moses.

00:37:17.839 --> 00:37:25.279
Your face will shine like Moses's did with

00:37:22.320 --> 00:37:27.760
the glory of the Lord. He said, 'But you

00:37:25.280 --> 00:37:32.000
will have to be more dead to self than ever—dead

00:37:27.760 --> 00:37:34.960
to self so much so that it

00:37:32.000 --> 00:37:38.160
is a burning sacrifice that comes up

00:37:34.960 --> 00:37:40.160
before My altar. I will share

00:37:38.160 --> 00:37:42.879
My glory with no one.'He kept telling

00:37:40.160 --> 00:37:47.839
me this week, 'But I'm putting in My

00:37:42.880 --> 00:37:50.880
dream team, the finals. This is it—the

00:37:47.839 --> 00:37:54.000
last hurrah, the

00:37:50.880 --> 00:37:57.280
fireworks show, the great finale,

00:37:54.000 --> 00:38:00.000
the dream team.'And you're about to

00:37:57.280 --> 00:38:03.040
see signs and wonders. I told you I

00:38:00.000 --> 00:38:05.119
saw Jesus and those chariots of fire with

00:38:03.040 --> 00:38:07.200
presents and mantles that we've never

00:38:05.119 --> 00:38:09.839
seen before were on those chariots of

00:38:07.200 --> 00:38:13.200
fire. When I went to heaven, I could

00:38:09.839 --> 00:38:16.720
see the silos full of body parts: black

00:38:13.200 --> 00:38:19.919
arms, white arms, black noses, green

00:38:16.720 --> 00:38:22.078
eyes, brown eyes, blue eyes, black eyes—all kinds of different colored eyes,

00:38:19.920 --> 00:38:23.920
all kinds of different colored

00:38:22.079 --> 00:38:26.960
skin in

00:38:23.920 --> 00:38:29.200
silos. The body parts were all in

00:38:26.960 --> 00:38:32.880
these silos

00:38:29.200 --> 00:38:36.480
for creative miracles,

00:38:32.880 --> 00:38:38.640
creative signs and wonders. And I saw

00:38:36.480 --> 00:38:39.920
things in these silos

00:38:38.640 --> 00:38:42.960
that people have been believing

00:38:39.920 --> 00:38:45.280
for, and I saw the silos being emptied.

00:38:42.960 --> 00:38:47.680
He said, 'There's no reason for them to

00:38:45.280 --> 00:38:50.560
be full up here, son, because you don't need them

00:38:47.680 --> 00:38:54.319
when you come up here.

00:38:50.560 --> 00:38:57.759
I'm releasing the silos

00:38:54.320 --> 00:39:00.800
for this last outpouring.'I saw a

00:38:57.760 --> 00:39:02.880
glorious wave of the glory of God that

00:39:00.800 --> 00:39:04.000
was coming, and I saw mantles of people.

00:39:02.880 --> 00:39:06.880
Everybody's

00:39:04.000 --> 00:39:08.960
always trying to say, 'Well, I want Oral Roberts's

00:39:06.880 --> 00:39:13.359
mantle back from when he was

00:39:08.960 --> 00:39:16.079
alive.'No,

00:39:13.359 --> 00:39:17.920
God's not a cookie-cutter. You were

00:39:16.079 --> 00:39:20.240
fearfully and wonderfully made. You

00:39:17.920 --> 00:39:23.200
don't need Brother So-and-So's

00:39:20.240 --> 00:39:26.319
mantle; you have what God's put on you.

00:39:23.200 --> 00:39:29.200
You don't need Kenneth Hagin's

00:39:26.320 --> 00:39:30.800
mantle or Kathryn Kuhlman's

00:39:29.200 --> 00:39:32.879
mantle. People wonder, 'Well, I wonder who got her

00:39:30.800 --> 00:39:36.240
mantle? Was it Benny Hinn or whoever?'Billy Burke, or whoever is there—I can tell you they might operate similarly, but I can assure you

00:39:32.880 --> 00:39:38.079
Billy Burke

00:39:36.240 --> 00:39:39.759
is

00:39:39.760 --> 00:39:43.440
Billy Burke.

00:39:42.000 --> 00:39:44.640
I'm personal

00:39:43.440 --> 00:39:45.920
friends with Billy Burke, and I'm

00:39:44.640 --> 00:39:48.160
telling you, the man walks in a healing mantle

00:39:45.920 --> 00:39:49.920
that is amazing. Yes, it's

00:39:48.160 --> 00:39:52.160
similar to Kathryn Kuhlman's—similar,

00:39:49.920 --> 00:39:54.320
I'm going to say that—but

00:39:52.160 --> 00:39:57.440
he is fearfully and wonderfully made by

00:39:54.320 --> 00:39:59.520
himself, and it's beautiful to talk to him

00:39:57.440 --> 00:40:01.680
on the phone. There are people who carry

00:39:59.520 --> 00:40:04.079
prayer mantles; there are people who carry

00:40:01.680 --> 00:40:06.319
things. When the Lord talked

00:40:04.079 --> 00:40:08.800
to me about Jeannie Wilkerson and the impartations

00:40:06.320 --> 00:40:11.359
people receive, He said

00:40:08.800 --> 00:40:14.400
this is

00:40:11.359 --> 00:40:18.400
something that we've never seen before.

00:40:14.400 --> 00:40:20.720
We cannot camp around old wineskins,

00:40:18.400 --> 00:40:23.520
for God is about to do something we've

00:40:20.720 --> 00:40:26.640
never seen before.

00:40:23.520 --> 00:40:30.759
As I saw those chariots of fire

00:40:26.640 --> 00:40:30.759
delivering those packages,

00:40:30.880 --> 00:40:35.680
He reminded me of it.

00:40:33.760 --> 00:40:38.880
He said, 'Do you remember December

00:40:35.680 --> 00:40:41.598
25th, whenever you were giving your gifts

00:40:38.880 --> 00:40:43.200
to your kids? I was giving My gifts to

00:40:41.599 --> 00:40:45.200
Mine.'Not

00:40:43.200 --> 00:40:47.359
all of those chariots of fire were

00:40:45.200 --> 00:40:48.560
able to deliver those gifts because the people

00:40:47.359 --> 00:40:51.200
weren't ready for them and they

00:40:48.560 --> 00:40:52.720
refused to take them. I saw the

00:40:51.200 --> 00:40:54.560
chariot of fire turn back around and go

00:40:52.720 --> 00:40:56.399
back into heaven with that package

00:40:54.560 --> 00:40:59.119
on the back because they wouldn't take

00:40:56.400 --> 00:41:01.119
the gift.

00:40:59.119 --> 00:41:02.960
Freely we've been given; freely we give

00:41:01.119 --> 00:41:04.560
it out. God is not a man;

00:41:02.960 --> 00:41:07.440
He's not a God that forces you to do

00:41:04.560 --> 00:41:09.759
anything. He's a gentleman.

00:41:07.440 --> 00:41:13.200
The Lord showed me these gifts and

00:41:09.760 --> 00:41:15.920
callings of new mantles, like it was

00:41:13.200 --> 00:41:17.919
with William Seymour. They were the

00:41:15.920 --> 00:41:19.760
original; they were the dream team of

00:41:17.920 --> 00:41:22.240
that generation.

00:41:19.760 --> 00:41:25.599
But God said, 'I'm bringing My dream

00:41:22.240 --> 00:41:27.919
team of this generation,'with

00:41:25.599 --> 00:41:30.720
signs and wonders and mantles

00:41:27.920 --> 00:41:32.400
that have never been seen before,

00:41:30.720 --> 00:41:33.759
just like it was when Kathryn Kuhlman

00:41:32.400 --> 00:41:35.760
walked on the scene. Nobody had seen

00:41:33.760 --> 00:41:37.200
that before. Nobody saw a woman wear a

00:41:35.760 --> 00:41:39.440
white dress like that and flow around,

00:41:37.200 --> 00:41:42.240
and the Holy Spirit and do all that

00:41:39.440 --> 00:41:45.359
she did. Nobody had seen that before.

00:41:42.240 --> 00:41:47.279
She was original; she wasn't an echo.

00:41:45.359 --> 00:41:49.920
And the Lord said, "I'm raising up not

00:41:47.280 --> 00:41:51.440
echoes, Brandon. I'm raising up new

00:41:49.920 --> 00:41:53.760
voices

00:41:51.440 --> 00:41:56.560
that will take the baton from the elders,

00:41:53.760 --> 00:41:59.200
the elder generation, and march

00:41:56.560 --> 00:42:01.200
on, soldier, onward Christian soldier."He

00:41:59.200 --> 00:42:04.078
said, "Do you understand what I'm

00:42:01.200 --> 00:42:07.279
trying to tell you all?

00:42:04.079 --> 00:42:09.760
Stop looking to the past and look to

00:42:07.280 --> 00:42:11.920
what's coming, what God has for you to

00:42:09.760 --> 00:42:15.280
do. You're a closer. You're built for

00:42:11.920 --> 00:42:17.520
pressure. God saved the best for last.

00:42:15.280 --> 00:42:22.160
We will be the generation that does not

00:42:17.520 --> 00:42:25.520
taste death, but we move with the cloud.

00:42:22.160 --> 00:42:28.078
Where is God calling you to be?

00:42:25.520 --> 00:42:30.480
Don't camp around what you used to do

00:42:28.079 --> 00:42:32.800
and what you used to think you were.

00:42:30.480 --> 00:42:35.200
Find out God's word for the now, the word for

00:42:32.800 --> 00:42:37.920
today, and go to the place called there.

00:42:35.200 --> 00:42:40.640
For when the provision dries up and the

00:42:37.920 --> 00:42:42.800
Riverbrook dries up and the raven stops

00:42:40.640 --> 00:42:47.200
coming and giving you the food, you have

00:42:42.800 --> 00:42:49.760
to go to the place called there.

00:42:47.200 --> 00:42:52.160
Where is the provision that God has for

00:42:49.760 --> 00:42:55.040
your ministry? And where is what God has

00:42:52.160 --> 00:42:58.000
for you today? Because God is a God of

00:42:55.040 --> 00:43:00.400
abundant supply and there is no lack in

00:42:58.000 --> 00:43:04.079
Him. If you're a giver and you're a sower,"He

00:43:00.400 --> 00:43:06.000
said, "I'll provide 30, 60, and 100-fold."Either

00:43:04.079 --> 00:43:08.240
you believe it or you

00:43:06.000 --> 00:43:10.800
don't. But if there's no bountiful

00:43:08.240 --> 00:43:13.359
supply, He said, "You got to go to the

00:43:10.800 --> 00:43:16.800
Word to where I said go to the place

00:43:13.359 --> 00:43:19.839
called there, Brandon.

00:43:16.800 --> 00:43:22.000
Go and travel with

00:43:19.839 --> 00:43:24.000
the glory. For where

00:43:22.000 --> 00:43:26.400
there's glory, there's abundance."The manna

00:43:24.000 --> 00:43:28.640
always showed up every morning for

00:43:26.400 --> 00:43:30.960
the kids.

00:43:28.640 --> 00:43:32.560
He always took care of His kids. And if

00:43:30.960 --> 00:43:34.800
He took care of them in the Old

00:43:32.560 --> 00:43:36.400
Testament, how much more will He take

00:43:34.800 --> 00:43:39.280
care of you in the New. That's what He

00:43:36.400 --> 00:43:42.240
said to me. But you have to be where the

00:43:39.280 --> 00:43:44.079
glory cloud's at. For where the

00:43:42.240 --> 00:43:47.200
glory cloud's at, that's where His

00:43:44.079 --> 00:43:49.440
abundant supply is. And He said, "A lot

00:43:47.200 --> 00:43:51.118
of people are not in that place, and

00:43:49.440 --> 00:43:52.720
that's why they're struggling."And He

00:43:51.119 --> 00:43:54.480
said, "Break off the things of the old

00:43:52.720 --> 00:43:56.560
and what you used to know."And He said,

00:43:54.480 --> 00:43:59.280
"Brandon, I'm going. It might

00:43:56.560 --> 00:44:01.359
be time to trim some fat.

00:43:59.280 --> 00:44:03.280
Trim some fat."He

00:44:01.359 --> 00:44:04.960
said, "Just because

00:44:03.280 --> 00:44:08.720
it worked back then doesn't mean it's

00:44:04.960 --> 00:44:11.280
for today. And as the glory intensifies,

00:44:08.720 --> 00:44:15.040
I'll bring more supply."And

00:44:11.280 --> 00:44:17.040
I got so stirred up inside

00:44:15.040 --> 00:44:19.839
about this, about my own ministry and

00:44:17.040 --> 00:44:23.119
about what He's saying about me. He

00:44:19.839 --> 00:44:26.078
said, "I'm the God of more than enough.

00:44:23.119 --> 00:44:28.160
The provision's always there.

00:44:26.079 --> 00:44:30.640
The gold coin was in the fish's mouth,

00:44:28.160 --> 00:44:32.480
son.

00:44:30.640 --> 00:44:35.520
They never lacked anything. Even my

00:44:32.480 --> 00:44:38.880
disciples, I took care of them always.

00:44:35.520 --> 00:44:43.200
Go to the place called there, Brandon.

00:44:38.880 --> 00:44:45.599
Always be at the place called there.

00:44:43.200 --> 00:44:48.799
You can sit by the Riverbrook and worry

00:44:45.599 --> 00:44:50.560
about why it dried up

00:44:48.800 --> 00:44:52.640
and look at the river as it flows and

00:44:50.560 --> 00:44:56.319
go, 'What? It all went away.'The raven doesn't

00:44:52.640 --> 00:44:59.200
come anymore because

00:44:56.319 --> 00:45:01.119
you got to go to the widow and I'll

00:44:59.200 --> 00:45:03.040
take care of you there. I'll get

00:45:01.119 --> 00:45:05.359
the cake and the little oil, and abundant

00:45:03.040 --> 00:45:08.160
supply came on it. The moment he blessed

00:45:05.359 --> 00:45:10.078
it and she sowed the seed,

00:45:08.160 --> 00:45:11.839
the abundant supply came to pay off our

00:45:10.079 --> 00:45:13.200
debts. The abundant supply came that

00:45:11.839 --> 00:45:16.319
they had more than enough. They didn't

00:45:13.200 --> 00:45:18.319
starve and die. He had more than enough. Go and

00:45:16.319 --> 00:45:21.440
sell all this. Look what I did. Boom.

00:45:18.319 --> 00:45:23.359
Find every pot, every vessel,

00:45:21.440 --> 00:45:26.079
everything, and I'm going to fill

00:45:23.359 --> 00:45:28.160
it to the top, to the overflow,

00:45:26.079 --> 00:45:29.680
to the point where she was going and

00:45:28.160 --> 00:45:32.640
borrowing vessels. The man of God is here. The Prophet of God is here, and where

