00:57:31.280 --> 00:57:36.480
honors patterns of faithfulness, and

00:57:33.599 --> 00:57:39.760
hell dreads them. If you want sustained

00:57:36.480 --> 00:57:42.640
glory, build sustained prayer. Your

00:57:39.760 --> 00:57:45.280
legacy is built in repetition. No one

00:57:42.640 --> 00:57:47.839
writes stories about daily groaning. No

00:57:45.280 --> 00:57:50.960
one celebrates the private fasts or the

00:57:47.839 --> 00:57:55.119
weekly watches, but heaven records every

00:57:50.960 --> 00:57:57.359
act of consistency. Revival legacy isn't

00:57:55.119 --> 00:58:00.640
built in one moment. It's built in

00:57:57.359 --> 00:58:03.040
thousands of hidden ones. One prayer may

00:58:00.640 --> 00:58:06.480
start the fire, but faithfulness keeps

00:58:03.040 --> 00:58:08.880
it burning. How to become consistent in

00:58:06.480 --> 00:58:10.960
intercession: Set your times.

00:58:08.880 --> 00:58:14.240
Appointments with God create divine

00:58:10.960 --> 00:58:17.119
momentum. Build sacred habits. Make

00:58:14.240 --> 00:58:20.078
prayer a lifestyle, not a reaction.

00:58:17.119 --> 00:58:22.640
Refuse to be moved. Don't let feelings

00:58:20.079 --> 00:58:25.680
decide your faithfulness.

00:58:22.640 --> 00:58:28.078
Lord of glory, I choose consistency. I

00:58:25.680 --> 00:58:30.720
won't be an off-again, on-again. I won't

00:58:28.079 --> 00:58:34.559
burn bright for a moment and then fade.

00:58:30.720 --> 00:58:37.680
Make me steady, daily, reliable. Let my

00:58:34.559 --> 00:58:40.480
prayers become an unshakable rhythm of

00:58:37.680 --> 00:58:43.118
fire. I want to be known in heaven for

00:58:40.480 --> 00:58:45.200
my faithfulness. Let hell fear my

00:58:43.119 --> 00:58:47.599
schedule.

00:58:45.200 --> 00:58:49.359
When you become a prayer, intercession

00:58:47.599 --> 00:58:52.240
doesn't just come through you, it

00:58:49.359 --> 00:58:54.720
becomes you. There came a moment when I

00:58:52.240 --> 00:58:58.319
stopped praying about things. I became

00:58:54.720 --> 00:59:01.520
the prayer. My life was the groan. My

00:58:58.319 --> 00:59:04.799
breath was the incense. I wasn't just

00:59:01.520 --> 00:59:06.799
asking. I was embodying the burden. When

00:59:04.799 --> 00:59:10.240
you become the prayer, you stop

00:59:06.799 --> 00:59:12.319
performing and start

00:59:28.400 --> 00:59:33.920
burning."Many

00:59:59.440 --> 01:00:05.280
thought I was

01:00:01.760 --> 01:00:07.839
strange, intense, too serious. But I

01:00:05.280 --> 01:00:12.160
wasn't living for them. I was under

01:00:07.839 --> 01:00:14.799
divine arrest, marked by God, set apart

01:00:12.160 --> 01:00:17.359
for something holy. The spirit had

01:00:14.799 --> 01:00:20.640
claimed my life and I surrendered to the

01:00:17.359 --> 01:00:23.839
calling. Don't expect to be understood.

01:00:20.640 --> 01:00:27.118
Expect to be used. How to live as a

01:00:23.839 --> 01:00:29.520
walking prayer: let go of normal.

01:00:27.119 --> 01:00:32.559
Intercessors often live a

01:00:29.520 --> 01:00:35.359
consecrated, misunderstood life. Yield

01:00:32.559 --> 01:00:38.799
fully. Don't ask for revival without

01:00:35.359 --> 01:00:41.359
giving God your entire schedule. Burn

01:00:38.799 --> 01:00:44.640
continuously. Stay in the posture of

01:00:41.359 --> 01:00:47.440
surrender until you embody the burden.

01:00:44.640 --> 01:00:50.078
Holy Spirit, I don't just want to pray.

01:00:47.440 --> 01:00:53.119
I want to become the prayer. Make my

01:00:50.079 --> 01:00:56.960
life an altar. Let my breath carry your

01:00:53.119 --> 01:01:00.240
groan. Possess my time, my energy, my

01:00:56.960 --> 01:01:03.040
soul. I give up normal to carry the

01:01:00.240 --> 01:01:05.839
extraordinary. Let me be a walking

01:01:03.040 --> 01:01:09.359
intercession. Let others encounter you

01:01:05.839 --> 01:01:11.680
through the fire that burns in me.

01:01:09.359 --> 01:01:14.799
Crying out for a generation you'll

01:01:11.680 --> 01:01:16.640
never meet. True intercessors sow for

01:01:14.799 --> 01:01:18.400
what they may never see.

01:01:16.640 --> 01:01:20.720
See right here, Rachel Teafatiller.

01:01:18.400 --> 01:01:22.640
Some of the

01:01:20.720 --> 01:01:25.439
people are glorious; some of these

01:01:22.640 --> 01:01:27.839
elders went on, but they were

01:01:25.440 --> 01:01:29.920
deep prayer warriors that prayed for the

01:01:27.839 --> 01:01:32.078
revival that we're about to have, and

01:01:29.920 --> 01:01:34.400
they never got to taste it. So,

01:01:32.079 --> 01:01:36.079
this is what I thought about her

01:01:34.400 --> 01:01:38.880
whenever Rachel Teafatiller and these

01:01:36.079 --> 01:01:40.799
others prayed for this revival and

01:01:38.880 --> 01:01:42.880
praying for a glorious church. Now, read

01:01:40.799 --> 01:01:44.640
that again. Read that again.

01:01:42.880 --> 01:01:46.960
I'm just trying to, you know,

01:01:44.640 --> 01:01:48.799
it's like Lucy—she never got

01:01:46.960 --> 01:01:52.799
to taste the revival. Here we are. This

01:01:48.799 --> 01:01:57.000
is it. True intercessors sow for

01:01:52.799 --> 01:01:57.000
what they may never see.

01:01:57.440 --> 01:02:01.920
I didn't just pray for the revival at

01:01:59.599 --> 01:02:04.720
hand. I prayed for the generations to

01:02:01.920 --> 01:02:08.079
come. I cried out for children I'll never

01:02:04.720 --> 01:02:10.720
meet, for preachers not yet born, for

01:02:08.079 --> 01:02:13.040
nations yet to hear. My prayers

01:02:10.720 --> 01:02:16.640
stretched into the future and seeded

01:02:13.040 --> 01:02:20.558
awakening for decades beyond me. Legacy

01:02:16.640 --> 01:02:22.400
intercession is unselfish. It's eternal.

01:02:20.559 --> 01:02:25.760
The spirit will burden you for the

01:02:22.400 --> 01:02:28.640
unseen. Many of my groans weren't even

01:02:25.760 --> 01:02:31.119
for the moment. They were for you—yes,

01:02:28.640 --> 01:02:33.440
you reading this now. I groaned for your

01:02:31.119 --> 01:02:36.000
breakthrough long before you were born.

01:02:33.440 --> 01:02:39.280
Because God doesn't see time; He sees

01:02:36.000 --> 01:02:41.839
harvest. He places future cries in

01:02:39.280 --> 01:02:44.559
present intercessors. You want to be

01:02:41.839 --> 01:02:46.240
used by God? Then pray beyond your own

01:02:44.559 --> 01:02:49.119
timeline.

01:02:46.240 --> 01:02:51.359
Your ceiling becomes their floor. Every

01:02:49.119 --> 01:02:53.760
generation of intercessors lays the

01:02:51.359 --> 01:02:56.160
foundation for the next. The groans you

01:02:53.760 --> 01:02:58.480
release now become the fire others walk

01:02:56.160 --> 01:03:00.960
in later. You may never see their

01:02:58.480 --> 01:03:03.920
revival, but your cry built the path

01:03:00.960 --> 01:03:05.760
they'll walk on. If you'll sow now,

01:03:03.920 --> 01:03:07.920
they'll reap later, and heaven will

01:03:05.760 --> 01:03:10.400
credit your faith.

01:03:07.920 --> 01:03:13.200
How to intercede for the future? Ask God

01:03:10.400 --> 01:03:15.920
for a generational burden. Let your heart

01:03:13.200 --> 01:03:18.879
stretch beyond the moment. Declare

01:03:15.920 --> 01:03:21.760
revival over tomorrow's leaders. Speak

01:03:18.880 --> 01:03:24.880
into the future by the spirit.

01:03:21.760 --> 01:03:27.680
Sacrificially give today for what only

01:03:24.880 --> 01:03:30.240
eternity will measure.

01:03:27.680 --> 01:03:32.720
Eternal God, give me a burden for the

01:03:30.240 --> 01:03:36.078
generations I'll never meet. Let me sow

01:03:32.720 --> 01:03:39.038
revival now for souls yet unborn. Let my

01:03:36.079 --> 01:03:41.839
prayers echo into the future. Mark this

01:03:39.039 --> 01:03:45.280
season with groans that outlive me. Let

01:03:41.839 --> 01:03:48.000
others run into the fire I lit. I choose

01:03:45.280 --> 01:03:50.079
to be a seed of awakening for now and

01:03:48.000 --> 01:03:52.240
forever.

01:03:50.079 --> 01:03:55.520
The joy of carrying what others can't

01:03:52.240 --> 01:03:58.720
see. There is joy in the groan. Yes, I

01:03:55.520 --> 01:04:02.160
wept. Yes, I travailed. Yes, I bled in

01:03:58.720 --> 01:04:05.279
the spirit. But hear me, there was joy—deep,

01:04:02.160 --> 01:04:07.680
unshakable joy—because I knew I

01:04:05.280 --> 01:04:10.720
was carrying something eternal. I was

01:04:07.680 --> 01:04:12.399
housing a holy burden. I was chosen by

01:04:10.720 --> 01:04:14.959
God to birth what others would

01:04:12.400 --> 01:04:16.799
celebrate. You will never be more

01:04:14.960 --> 01:04:19.680
fulfilled than when you carry God's

01:04:16.799 --> 01:04:22.240
burden with joy. Intercession isn't

01:04:19.680 --> 01:04:24.078
depression. It's divine partnership.

01:04:22.240 --> 01:04:27.439
Some think the groan is heavy and

01:04:24.079 --> 01:04:30.160
miserable. No, it is holy. It is

01:04:27.440 --> 01:04:33.520
glorious. The burden of the Lord is

01:04:30.160 --> 01:04:36.160
intense, but it is never without joy. He

01:04:33.520 --> 01:04:39.200
invites us to partner with him in the

01:04:36.160 --> 01:04:41.200
sacred act of transformation.

01:04:39.200 --> 01:04:44.078
And when you realize heaven trusts you

01:04:41.200 --> 01:04:47.520
with something, that precious joy

01:04:44.079 --> 01:04:50.640
explodes in your soul. The joy of the

01:04:47.520 --> 01:04:53.359
unseen assignment. They didn't clap for

01:04:50.640 --> 01:04:56.240
me. They didn't know my name, but heaven

01:04:53.359 --> 01:04:59.038
did. And that joy—the joy of knowing I obeyed—was

01:04:56.240 --> 01:05:02.319
stronger than any applause.

01:04:59.039 --> 01:05:04.480
I had joy unspeakable and full of glory

01:05:02.319 --> 01:05:06.799
because I was used by God to birth what

01:05:04.480 --> 01:05:09.599
others would never understand. And I

01:05:06.799 --> 01:05:12.240
wouldn't trade it for anything. How to

01:05:09.599 --> 01:05:14.720
embrace joy in the throne: recognize

01:05:12.240 --> 01:05:17.919
heaven's trust. You've been chosen to

01:05:14.720 --> 01:05:20.240
carry holy things. Celebrate obedience.

01:05:17.920 --> 01:05:23.039
Let your joy be rooted in faithfulness,

01:05:20.240 --> 01:05:26.240
not visibility. Receive the smile of

01:05:23.039 --> 01:05:28.640
God. His pleasure is your strength.

01:05:26.240 --> 01:05:31.520
Father, thank you for trusting me with a

01:05:28.640 --> 01:05:34.000
holy burden. I say yes to

01:05:31.520 --> 01:05:36.960
the groan and yes to the joy that comes

01:05:34.000 --> 01:05:39.920
with it. Let me feel your delight as I

01:05:36.960 --> 01:05:42.640
press into the unseen places. I receive

01:05:39.920 --> 01:05:44.880
the joy of obedience. Let my soul

01:05:42.640 --> 01:05:47.839
rejoice in carrying what few will ever

01:05:44.880 --> 01:05:50.400
understand.

01:05:47.839 --> 01:05:52.720
When the burden becomes your identity,

01:05:50.400 --> 01:05:55.520
you stop carrying the burden; it carries

01:05:52.720 --> 01:05:57.759
you. There comes a point in the life of an

01:05:55.520 --> 01:06:00.640
intercessor when you no longer say, 'I

01:05:57.760 --> 01:06:03.839
have a burden.'Instead, you realize the

01:06:00.640 --> 01:06:06.319
burden has you. You've become one with

01:06:03.839 --> 01:06:08.720
the groan. You're no longer dipping in

01:06:06.319 --> 01:06:11.599
and out of prayer. You are prayer. The

01:06:08.720 --> 01:06:14.000
ache of God has marked you. That's where

01:06:11.599 --> 01:06:16.880
I lived. I didn't visit

01:06:14.000 --> 01:06:18.880
intercession. I became intercession.

01:06:16.880 --> 01:06:21.200
You'll never be the same once the burden

01:06:18.880 --> 01:06:23.599
takes root in your spirit. Your

01:06:21.200 --> 01:06:26.240
assignment becomes your atmosphere. When

01:06:23.599 --> 01:06:29.039
I entered a city, I didn't have to ask

01:06:26.240 --> 01:06:31.439
what the burden was. I felt it. Because

01:06:29.039 --> 01:06:34.079
the intercessor carries more than prayer

01:06:31.440 --> 01:06:36.000
points. They carry atmospheres. When

01:06:34.079 --> 01:06:38.559
you're saturated in the spirit, your

01:06:36.000 --> 01:06:40.880
very presence becomes catalytic.

01:06:38.559 --> 01:06:44.000
Conviction begins before the

01:06:40.880 --> 01:06:47.680
message is preached. Glory descends

01:06:44.000 --> 01:06:51.119
before the meeting begins.

01:06:47.680 --> 01:06:54.319
Diana, I love it.

01:06:51.119 --> 01:06:56.960
The burden becomes a lens through which

01:06:54.319 --> 01:06:59.038
you see everything. When God trusts you

01:06:56.960 --> 01:07:00.960
with his groan, there is no greater

01:06:59.039 --> 01:07:03.599
honor than to be trusted with God's

01:07:00.960 --> 01:07:06.079
burden. When he lets you feel what he

01:07:03.599 --> 01:07:08.240
feels, weep where he weeps, intercede

01:07:06.079 --> 01:07:12.119
where he longs to move, it means he has

01:07:08.240 --> 01:07:12.118
found a yielded vessel.

01:07:13.200 --> 01:07:16.879
The burden isn't a weight to escape.

01:07:15.200 --> 01:07:19.279
It's an invitation into divine

01:07:16.880 --> 01:07:22.480
partnership. How to walk in your

01:07:19.280 --> 01:07:24.799
intercessory identity: stop

01:07:22.480 --> 01:07:27.359
compartmentalizing prayer. Become a

01:07:24.799 --> 01:07:30.720
walking altar. Let the burden shape your

01:07:27.359 --> 01:07:32.480
schedule. Don't resist it. Lean into it.

01:07:30.720 --> 01:07:35.520
Wear the groaning with joy. It means

01:07:32.480 --> 01:07:37.680
you've been trusted with heaven's ache.

01:07:35.520 --> 01:07:39.920
Lord, I don't want to carry a temporary

01:07:37.680 --> 01:07:42.640
burden. I want to become the intercessor

01:07:39.920 --> 01:07:45.119
you can trust. Let the weight of revival

01:07:42.640 --> 01:07:48.000
become my identity. Let your groan live

01:07:45.119 --> 01:07:50.000
inside me. Make me one with your ache. I

01:07:48.000 --> 01:07:52.079
say yes to the burden, the calling, and

01:07:50.000 --> 01:07:54.240
the cost.

01:07:52.079 --> 01:07:56.640
Praying until the glory dwells. Not just

01:07:54.240 --> 01:07:58.558
a visit, but a habitation. I wasn't

01:07:56.640 --> 01:08:02.000
praying for an event; I was crying out

01:07:58.559 --> 01:08:04.480
for a habitation. I didn't want a drop.

01:08:02.000 --> 01:08:06.960
I wanted a deluge. I didn't want God to

01:08:04.480 --> 01:08:09.039
visit. I wanted him to dwell. And for

01:08:06.960 --> 01:08:11.680
that, I groaned until the air shifted

01:08:09.039 --> 01:08:15.280
and stayed. Many pray for revival to

01:08:11.680 --> 01:08:17.759
fall. Few pray for it to rest. My cry

01:08:15.280 --> 01:08:20.560
was simple: Stay, Lord. Don't just come;

01:08:17.759 --> 01:08:23.359
remain. Only intercessors can host the

01:08:20.560 --> 01:08:25.120
glory long term. Preachers can ignite,

01:08:23.359 --> 01:08:27.679
worshippers can stir, but only

01:08:25.120 --> 01:08:30.080
intercessors can host because it takes

01:08:27.679 --> 01:08:32.880
groaning, covering, warring, and weeping

01:08:30.080 --> 01:08:36.479
to protect what God releases. Glory

01:08:32.880 --> 01:08:38.319
lingers where prayer saturates the soil.

01:08:36.479 --> 01:08:40.158
You want revival to remain in your

01:08:38.319 --> 01:08:43.120
church? Then keep the furnace of

01:08:40.158 --> 01:08:45.519
intercession burning non-stop.

01:08:43.120 --> 01:08:47.358
You become the ark that carries him. I

01:08:45.520 --> 01:08:49.279
longed to be a man that God could dwell with—not

01:08:47.359 --> 01:08:52.000
just touch occasionally, but

01:08:49.279 --> 01:08:54.239
live inside continuously. I became a

01:08:52.000 --> 01:08:56.799
walking tabernacle. I guarded his

01:08:54.238 --> 01:08:59.278
presence. I made my life his resting

01:08:56.799 --> 01:09:01.759
place. That's what sustained the glory

01:08:59.279 --> 01:09:03.839
in Finney's meetings. It wasn't structure.

01:09:01.759 --> 01:09:05.679
It was saturation.

01:09:03.839 --> 01:09:08.080
How to pray for habitation, not just

01:09:05.679 --> 01:09:10.319
visitation: guard the atmosphere. Don't

01:09:08.080 --> 01:09:10.640
let glory be treated casually. Keep

01:09:10.319 --> 01:09:13.120
praying.

01:09:10.640 --> 01:09:15.920
Did you hear that? When the

01:09:13.120 --> 01:09:17.439
Lord said to us, 'What you're about to

01:09:15.920 --> 01:09:19.600
see,

01:09:17.439 --> 01:09:21.839
do not take it for granted and

01:09:19.600 --> 01:09:25.120
let it become casual.

01:09:21.839 --> 01:09:27.359
You must honor the glory what's about to

01:09:25.120 --> 01:09:29.278
be displayed in the atmosphere of

01:09:27.359 --> 01:09:30.799
your churches and your buildings.'Don't

01:09:29.279 --> 01:09:33.199
take it as casual.

01:09:30.799 --> 01:09:37.120
Guard the

01:09:33.198 --> 01:09:39.198
atmosphere. Do not let the glory be

01:09:37.120 --> 01:09:42.000
treated casually.

01:09:39.198 --> 01:09:44.879
Don't dishonor it because you'll

01:09:42.000 --> 01:09:47.439
grieve the Holy Spirit. Every miracle—I

01:09:44.880 --> 01:09:49.600
don't care if it's a hangnail and

01:09:47.439 --> 01:09:50.960
somebody's gotten healed by something—you

01:09:49.600 --> 01:09:52.239
go, 'Well, that's not that big a deal.'Well,

01:09:50.960 --> 01:09:53.600
it was a big deal to them

01:09:52.238 --> 01:09:55.360
and it was a big deal to the Lord or he

01:09:53.600 --> 01:09:58.719
wouldn't have done it. He cares

01:09:55.360 --> 01:10:00.799
about all of it. Honor everything that's

01:09:58.719 --> 01:10:02.880
about to take place in the glorious

01:10:00.800 --> 01:10:07.719
Church.

01:10:02.880 --> 01:10:07.719
Hover over it and treat it as precious.

01:10:07.920 --> 01:10:13.600
Keep prayer central.

01:10:11.520 --> 01:10:17.199
Prayer must be the foundation, not the

01:10:13.600 --> 01:10:21.280
add-on. Ask God to dwell. Don't settle

01:10:17.199 --> 01:10:23.759
for anything less than lingering glory.

01:10:23.760 --> 01:10:27.199
Prayer must be the foundation

01:10:27.199 --> 01:10:31.120
in your church to keep the glory going,

01:10:29.360 --> 01:10:32.799
not an add-on. The glory

01:10:31.120 --> 01:10:34.719
is attached

01:10:32.800 --> 01:10:36.719
to the

01:10:34.719 --> 01:10:39.040
foundation

01:10:39.040 --> 01:10:42.280
of prayer.

01:10:42.320 --> 01:10:50.480
Ask God to dwell. Don't settle for

01:10:45.520 --> 01:10:52.800
anything less than lingering glory.

01:10:50.480 --> 01:10:55.280
I want more.

01:10:52.800 --> 01:10:58.080
It's not just going to be a one-and-done

01:10:55.280 --> 01:11:01.759
when we get there. We

01:10:58.080 --> 01:11:06.159
got it; it's here. And we won't stop praying until

01:11:01.760 --> 01:11:08.159
you make the devil a greasy spot.

01:11:06.159 --> 01:11:10.639
Smith Wigglesworth—it's

01:11:08.159 --> 01:11:13.120
like whenever you see—maybe it

01:11:10.640 --> 01:11:14.880
was Brother Hagin who said they saw this—you

01:11:13.120 --> 01:11:17.280
don't just, when you see the

01:11:14.880 --> 01:11:18.880
breakthrough, stop

01:11:17.280 --> 01:11:21.360
praying and giving God thanks

01:11:18.880 --> 01:11:24.880
and glory. You make him a greasy spot in

01:11:21.360 --> 01:11:26.639
the road like an old roadkill. You run

01:11:24.880 --> 01:11:28.960
that devil up, you back up and you hit

